{
  "texts": [
    "The GPT models have been used in various fields [20].",
    "The transfer-based various models [20][21][22][23][24][25][26][27] indicate the possibility of Artificial General Intelligence (AGI) models.",
    "However, even with current AI technology, a prominent data-based AI model is impossible in some research fields.",
    "For example, in the medical area and biomedical, big data are not always available other than big AI models.",
    "Researcher Andrew Wu states the importance of \"big AI in small data\" [28] and also certificated the necessity of efficient AI models for small datasets."
  ]
}